Package: wickraproof
Type: Package
Title: Deterministic Proof-of-Backtest Core
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-proof over its C ABI hub: create a stateless
    Prover, prove a (spec, data) pair to a canonical report and blake3 hash, and
    verify a proof - the same protocol as the CLI and every other binding.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-proof
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-proof/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-proof C ABI shared library (WKPROOF_LIB) and its
    header (WKPROOF_INC).
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
